`server.js` ‚Äî API + persistence + import/export/store normalization.
- `135` `normalizeEntry(row)` ‚Äî entry shape, `choreId`, `locationIds`.
- `163` `normalizeChorePreset(row)` ‚Äî validates title/points/color/scoringMode.
- `178` `normalizeChorePresets(arr)` ‚Äî array normalization for presets.
- `188` `normalizeQuickChoreIds(ids, presets)` ‚Äî validates quick bar ids against presets.
- `291` `normalizeStore(raw)` ‚Äî canonicalizes store object read from disk (`discordWebhook`, `discordReminderSentAt`, **`auditLog`**).
- `GET /api/audit` ‚Äî recent audit events (auth required); **`appendAudit`** on entry/settings/scheduled/import/discord user actions.
- `451` `app.get('/api/entries', ...)` ‚Äî list entries + `discordWebhook` for settings UI.
- Discord: `POST /api/discord-webhook/test`, `POST /api/discord-webhook/remind-now`; background timer sends overdue scheduled-chore reminders per `discordReminderSentAt`.
- `469`‚Äì`542` scheduled chore routes; `PUT /api/scheduled-chores/:id` supports title/interval/**startsOn** updates; `542` `POST .../complete` writes completion entry.
- `588` `app.put('/api/settings', ...)` ‚Äî settings write (people/presets/quick ids/locations).
- `657` `app.post('/api/import', ...)` ‚Äî import handler (replace/merge modes).
- `634` `app.get('/api/export', ...)` ‚Äî export.
- `768` `app.post('/api/entries', ...)` ‚Äî add entry (supports `choreId`, locations).
- `830` `app.put('/api/entries/:id', ...)` ‚Äî update entry.

`index.html` ‚Äî app shell, dialogs, script bootstrap.
- Settings: **Audit log** (`#auditLogList`, `#btnRefreshAuditLog`, `#auditLogStatus`); **Discord reminders** (`#discordWebhookEnabled`, `#discordWebhookUrl`, `#discordReminderInterval`, test / post-now buttons).
- `62`‚Äì`74` **analytics filters** `#analyticsPersonFilter`, `#analyticsLocationFilter`, hint `#analyticsFilterHint`; then `analytics-stats-row` / `statsGrid`, `statsGridPoints`.
- `76`‚Äì`94` `section-pair`: contributions (`barsArea`, `barsAreaPoints`) + heatmap `taskHeatmap`.
- `114`‚Äì`145` log form: `inChore`, `#scheduledLogSuggestionsWrap` / `#scheduledLogSuggestions` (due soon / overdue, preset title match), `inLocations`, quick log.
- `147`+ `log-mom-row`: **log filter** `#logSearch`, `#logList`, `momGrid`, `momGridPoints`.
- (approx.) `<script type="module" src="/js/chore-tracker.js">` at end of body.

`js/chore-tracker.js` ‚Äî thin entrypoint ‚Üí `main.js`.

`js/main.js` ‚Äî event wiring, auth/bootstrap, mutations, import/export UI flows.
- `205` `load()` ‚Äî fetch entries/settings, populate state.
- `295` `addEntry()` ‚Äî main add flow; semicolon payload, posts `/api/entries`.
- `fillChoreFromPreset(presetId)` ‚Äî sets `#inChore` + per-location locations (shared with quick log).
- `quickLogChore(presetId)` ‚Äî `fillChoreFromPreset` then `addEntry()`.
- `initScheduledLogSuggestions()` ‚Äî delegated click on `#scheduledLogSuggestions` ‚Üí fill + focus chore field.
- `saveScheduledStartDate(id, domKey)` ‚Äî updates scheduled chore `startsOn` from manage-list date input.
- `524` `startApp()` ‚Äî init date field, load, pick month, `render()`.
- `534` `bootstrap()` ‚Äî session check + app/login visibility.
- `#monthSelect` ‚Üí `switchMonth` (clears log search only).
- `#analyticsPersonFilter` / `#analyticsLocationFilter` `change` ‚Üí `app.analyticsPersonFilter` / `app.analyticsLocationFilter`, `render()`.
- `#logSearch` `input` ‚Üí `app.logSearchQuery`, `render()`.
- export/import handlers (`/api/export`, `/api/import`).
- `initQuickChores()`; `initScheduledLogSuggestions()`; chore suggest init nearby.

`js/presets.js` ‚Äî chore presets + quick log editor + payload resolution.
- `6` `syncChoreDatalists()` ‚Äî syncs edit dialog datalist.
- `16` `entryChorePoints(e)` ‚Äî points from preset + per_location √ó locations.
- `presetMatchingScheduledTitle(title)` ‚Äî preset match for scheduled log suggestions (exact, then small Levenshtein budget).
- `27` `resolveChorePayloadRows(raw)` ‚Äî splits `;` and resolves preset ids.
- `43` `saveChorePresetsAndQuick()` ‚Äî persists settings to `/api/settings`.
- preset/quick editors + `renderQuickChores`.

`js/chore-input-suggest.js` ‚Äî custom suggestion list for `#inChore`.
- `initChoreInputSuggest()` ‚Äî keyboard/mouse + segment-aware filtering.

`js/render.js` ‚Äî render pipeline for dashboard/log/scheduled views.
- `14` `entryMatchesAnalyticsFilters` / `entriesForAnalyticsMonth` ‚Äî person + location filters for stats/bars/heatmap/MoM (location = entry `locationIds` includes selected name).
- `entryMatchesLogSearch` ‚Äî log-only text filter (whitespace AND tokens).
- `countsByPerson` / `pointsByPerson` / `taskCountsByDay` ‚Äî use `entriesForAnalyticsMonth`.
- `fullRender()` ‚Äî analytics filters, dual stat grids, bars, heatmap, log list, **scheduled log suggestion buttons** (`scheduledStatus` overdue/today/soon + `presetMatchingScheduledTitle`), dual MoM, scheduled dashboard.
